Sentencas: High power density is required to commercialize solid oxide fuel cells for vehicular applications.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: In this work, high performance of metal supported solid oxide fuel cells (MS-SOFCs) is achieved via catalyst composition, electrode structure, and processing optimization.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: The full cell configuration consists of a dense ceramic electrolyte and porous ceramic backbones (electrodes) sandwiched between porous stainless steel metal supports.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: The conventional YSZ electrolyte and backbones are replaced with more conductive and thinner 10Sc1CeSZ ceramics.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: MS-SOFCs are co-sintered in a single step and subsequently infiltrated with nanocatalysts.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: Five categories of cathode catalysts are screened in full cells, including: perovskites, nickelates, praseodymium oxide, binary layered composites, and ternary layered composites.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: Various anode compositions are also tested.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: The conventional LSM cathode catalyst is replaced with more active Pr6O11 and the Ni content of the SDC-Ni anode is increased.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: The resulting cells achieve a peak power of 1.56, 2.0, and 2.85 W cm(-2) at 700, 750, and 800 degrees C, respectively, with 3%H2O/H-2 as fuel and cathode exposed to air.
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: Multiple cells show reproducible performance (P-max = 1.50 +/- 0.06 W cm(-2)) and OCV (1.10 +/- 0.02 V).
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes

Sentencas: The performance is further increased with cathode exposed to pure oxygen (2.0 W cm(-2) at 700 degrees C).
Titulo: High performance metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells with infiltrated electrodes
